      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_EFEEA7E0-22FB-0135-5E44-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To edit any section, click the <strong>Settings</strong> menu. To rename a section, click the <strong>Rename</strong> link [1]. To delete a section, click the <strong>Delete</strong> link [2]. To move a section, click the <strong>Move to...</strong> link [3]. You can also rearrange sections by clicking and dragging them.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
